      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a masterpiece of automotive engineering that remains in an unblemished state. Every aspect of this motorcar, from its pristine exterior finish to its meticulously preserved interior, reflects a standard of care that is seldom encountered. Rigorously inspected and verified for peak performance, this vehicle offers an uncompromising driving experience for those who settle for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
