    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom-ready condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it was first driven! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
