      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, an analog masterpiece of precision engineering. This example features the longitudinally mounted F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC inline-four, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp, short-throw 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. The chassis utilizes Honda\u2019s high-rigidity X-bone monocoque frame, paired with a sophisticated four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and factory-spec monotube dampers. Maintained in showroom state, the vehicle retains its original VIN-matched panels, flawless factory paint, and a pristine undercarriage. Mechanical health is absolute, with zero valve-train noise and a perfectly indexed steering rack.",
